title: Whitelist SushiSwap (SUSHI) with 200k BNT Coinvestment
body:
[Read the original proposal on Discourse](https://gov.bancor.network/t/proposal-whitelist-sushiswap-sushi-with-200k-bnt-coinvestment/2162)

TL;DR
=====

-   Proposal to whitelist SushiSwap SUSHI.
-   Co-investment of 200,000 BNT.
-   There are no apparent security concerns that would prohibit whitelist status.
-   There is no reason to doubt the legitimacy of the SushiSwap project. The SUSHI team includes Sam Bankman-Fried, CEO of derivatives exchange FTX and quantitative trading start-up Alameda Research.
-   The benefit to Bancor is clear. A pool with SUSHI will bring SUSHI holders to Bancor.

### [](https://gov.bancor.network/t/proposal-whitelist-sushiswap-sushi-with-200k-bnt-coinvestment/2162#project-website-httpssushicom-5)Project Website: <https://sushi.com/>

Deepest SUSHI pool is SUSHI/ETH on SushiSwap with a $485,911,790.85 liquidity. Uniswap SUSHI/ETH pool has a $1.04m liquidity.

[](https://gov.bancor.network/t/proposal-whitelist-sushiswap-sushi-with-200k-bnt-coinvestment/2162#token-security-6)Token Security
==================================================================================================================================

SUSHI does not have an elastic supply, or rebase mechanism. The SUSHI ERC-20 contracts do not have permissions that grant administrators unrestricted mint/burn capabilities.

SUSHI is a capped-supply token with a total supply of 250,000,000 tokens and circulating supply of 127,244,443 SUSHI. The top 15 contracts and addresses with the highest concentration of SUSHI tokens are the token vesting contracts, Binance, Houbi and OKEx.

![image](https://aws1.discourse-cdn.com/standard20/uploads/bancordao/optimized/1X/78147a500b2edb2704d64a765acb6c7183cd3edc_2_690x391.png)

[](https://gov.bancor.network/t/proposal-whitelist-sushiswap-sushi-with-200k-bnt-coinvestment/2162#project-7)Project
====================================================================================================================

SushiSwap (SUSHI) is an automated market maker, launched in September 2020 as a fork of Uniswap and aims to diversify the AMM market and also add additional features not previously present on Uniswap, such as increased rewards for network participants via its in-house token, SUSHI.

The platform takes a 0.3% cut from transactions occurring in its liquidity pools, while its SUSHI token is used to reward users portions of those fees. SUSHI also entitles users to governance rights.

[](https://gov.bancor.network/t/proposal-whitelist-sushiswap-sushi-with-200k-bnt-coinvestment/2162#tokenomics-8)Tokenomics
==========================================================================================================================

[SUSHI](https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/sushi) is a governance token that enables community governance over the Sushi ecosystem. This means that SUSHI holders can use their tokens to vote for platform proposals to further ecosystem initiatives.

The SUSHI token can be farmed by participating in the yield farming program on [sushi.com](http://sushi.com/).

The SUSHI token may also be staked across various platforms such as Sushi's very own, SushiBar, or can be used as collateral on platforms such as Sushi's Yearn ecosystem partner, Aave. When SUSHI tokens are staked, users receive xSUSHI in return. xSUSHI holders receive 0.05% of each and every swap completed on [sushi.com](http://sushi.com/)!

[](https://gov.bancor.network/t/proposal-whitelist-sushiswap-sushi-with-200k-bnt-coinvestment/2162#community-and-communication-9)Community and Communication
============================================================================================================================================================

SUSHI is active on [Reddit ](https://reddit.com/r/SushiSwap)and [Discord](https://discord.gg/hJ2p555). The SushiSwap team also operates official [Twitter](https://twitter.com/sushiswap) and [Medium](https://medium.com/@sushiswapchef/the-sushiswap-project-dd6eb80c6ba2) accounts. [Github](https://github.com/sushiswap/sushiswap) activity is frequent.

[](https://gov.bancor.network/t/proposal-whitelist-sushiswap-sushi-with-200k-bnt-coinvestment/2162#available-audits-10)Available Audits
=======================================================================================================================================

The SUSHI ERC-20 token contract is a standard OpenZeppelin contract. The SUSHI contracts have been audited by [Peckshield](https://github.com/peckshield/publications/blob/master/audit_reports/PeckShield-Audit-Report-SushiSwap-v1.0.pdf), [Quantstamp](https://github.com/quantstamp/sushiswap-security-review) and others.
